## Limitations

The analysis is based on available literature and may not capture the most recent changes in college tuition policies or economic conditions. Additionally, the perspectives included are primarily from U.S.-based sources, which may not fully represent global trends in higher education costs. Further research could explore the impact of recent policy changes and economic shifts on college affordability.